<div class="row d-flex justify-content-between">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-none d-sm-block card history">
    <h2 class="text-center">History</h2>
  </div>
  <div id="game-screen" class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column align-items-center screen">
    <img class="game-screen mb-3" width="700" src="/images/story/final_room3.jpg" />
    <p id="nar" class="card w-100">
    As you push open the creaking wooden door, you find yourself stepping into a
    some sort of living room that exudes a rustic charm. The hearth at the
    center of the room crackles with dancing flames, casting a warm and
    flickering light across the stone walls. The air is tinged with the
    comforting scent of burning firewood. The comfort is cut short as you see a
    large metallic door opposite of you. This door bears 3 large adornments that
    vertically descend the middle of the door. The top emblem shaped like a
    book, the middle shaped like a potion vial, and the last ominously shaped as
    a skull...
    </p>
    <div class="col-12">
      <form class="player-choices-form text-center">
        <button
          class="btn btn-danger choice-btn mb-1"
          id="choice1"
        >Go to the door.</button>
        <button
          class="d-none btn btn-success choice-btn mb-1"
          id="choice2"
        >Go to the door.</button>
        <button
          class=" d-none btn btn-success choice-btn mb-1"
          id="choice3"
        >Go to the chest.</button>
        <button
          class="d-none btn btn-success choice-btn mb-1"
          id="choice4"
        >Choice</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 d-none d-sm-block text-center card inventory p-2">
    <img class="avt mb-2" width="150" height="150" src="/images/avatars/avatar-{{player.avatar}}.png" />
    <h2>{{player.name}}</h2>
    <div class="col">
      <h3 class="text-center">Inventory</h3>
      <div class="col d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-around">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

